<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
.D           Bm        A       G
 Oldingda turib Xudoim orom topaman,
.D           Bm          A      G
 Bepoyon bu sevgingdan yuragim toʻlar.

[P1]
.      A       G
   // Kutarman Seni //

[C1]
.  D         G          D        Em
   Senga tiz choʻkaman, xayotim beraman,
.  Bm              G    A   D
   Faqat Seni deb, yashayman Iso.

[V2]
 Quchogʻing tomon talpinib deyman!: &quot;men zaif&quot;,
 Yagona Sening nigohing jonimga oro.</lyrics>
<key>D</key>
<title>Senga tiz choʻkaman ҲС62 ҲСХМ26</title>
